venue.name: Saint Anselm College - New Hampshire Institute of Politics

item.description: Per CNN, "Paul will address an audience of influential political notables at a forum hosted by the New Hampshire Institute of Politics at St. Anselm College. The event is considered a must-stop for candidates hoping to perform well in New Hampshire's first-in-the-nation primary." Paul is to speak from 8-9:30. Let's show the doctor and all those influential political notables how much support Dr. Paul has in New Hampshire.
item.name: Sign Wave for Ron's Politics and Eggs Event
